Pursuant to the Maryland Public Information Act, I hereby request the following records for every sworn officer and civilian member of the Rockville City Police Department for fiscal year 2022:
1. First and last name;
2. Unique sequence number;
3. Race;
4. Gender;
5. Hire date;
