City staff has collected the records in our custody that we believe are responsive to your request, and they are attached to this email.  Some information has been redacted pursuant to the Annotated Code of Maryland General Provisions Articles GP § 4-331. You may seek judicial review of the city's decision to withhold this information pursuant to § 4-362 of the General Provisions Article of the Annotated Code of Maryland.

Should you have any questions regarding this information, please do not hesitate to contact me.

Hunter Rooney
Administrative Assistant
City of Rockville
